node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on September 14, 2021. May be an image of tree and outdoors.

node.text: Making Some Huge Progress On The New Goonzquad Garage!!! The Scissor Lift Definitely Made Things Alot Smoother! Now We Just Need To Find Someone Who Can Replace The Craigslist Guy, He Got Fired! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on September 12, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text: We Made A Huge Decision! The New Goonzquad Garage Has Been In The Works For About A Year Now! Everything Is Finally Starting To Line Up! Only Thing Is We Don’t Wanna Wait Any Longer For The Structure To Get Built, Everyone Is Super Busy And The Price To Erect A Building Is Insane! We Might Be Crazy But We Decided To Put Up The Building Ourselves!!! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on September 09, 2021. May be an image of car and outdoors.

node.text: Woke Up In A Silly Goofy Mood The Other Day And Decided To Have A Drift Competition! Also Mom Said To Mow The Grass So Might As Well Do It In Style! Today’s Video Is Full Of Epicness! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on September 07, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, car and outdoors.

node.text: Got A Little Labor Day Special Video We Filmed Yesterday!!! Doing Some Good Ole Labor On Some Of The Other Builds And Also Had A Little Drift Session! Hope Y’all Had A Great Weekend And Can’t Wait To Show Y’all This Video!!! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on September 05, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: Tearing The TRX Completely Apart!!! Ended Up Ordering 3k In Dealership Parts, Now We Gotta Find The Expensive Stuff Probably Used! As For The Bed, We Might End Up Doing A Overland Flatbed, What Y’all Think?? #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on September 02, 2021. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: Finally Got The Engine And Trans Fitted Into The Camaro Perfectly!!! Now We’re Slapping On All The @holleyperformance Components On The Front Of The Engine! Also Threw Some Other Epic Touches At The Engine Bay Area! Now We Just Need A Few More Things And Soon It’ll Fire Up! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on August 31, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: Got A Parts List Together For The TRX!!! What Y’all Think The Damage Is? We Might Even Have To Return This Thing! Also Got It Started And It Sounds Pretty Good, Definitely Needs To Be Modified!!! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on August 29, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: Rebuilding A Wrecked 2021 Ram TRX!!! Finally Got One Of These Suckers! Let’s See What It’s All About!!! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on August 26, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, people standing and body of water.

node.text: Finally Making Some Major Moves On The New Goonzquad Garage!!! The Slab And Foundation Has Been The Most Difficult To Schedule, But Now It’s All Done! Also Huge Progress On The 67 Camaro, Engine Finally Mocked Up! New Video Will Be Up Soon!!! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on August 24, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: This Thing Is Getting Built!!! We Are Moving Into The Performance Side Of Things And This Is Where It Gets Epic! These @wilwooddiscbrakes Are So Perfect For This 67 Camaro, Especially After We Throw In The LT4 Engine! Also What Should We Name This Thing??? #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on August 22, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and car.

node.text: Finally Got This Sucker All Painted!!! This Paint Job Did Throw A Few Wild Things At Us, But We Managed To Get It Looking Right In The End! Can’t Wait To Get This Thing Buffed Out After We Get The New LT4 Engine Swapped In! This Is Where Things Start To Get Epic, Can’t Wait To Show Y’all!!! #newvideotoday #goonzquad
